major game additions ---------------------- -completely added multiple player pieces -user can now decide which piece to move after each roll -in making this, the player class has been changed to accomodate for this new feature. please note -------------- -there are more things that may have changed but are not noted above so please look inside the change log for the code -will now be working on the creation of snakes based on player judgements
Thanks guys
